imdb.plot outline: After the Rebeca (Barbara) catches innocent Eduardo kissing his first love Fernanda, she sends him to a far away land. Years pass and tragedy brings him back, vengeance fills his heart towards the Elizaldo family. And the series unfolds as he developed a secret identity in order to gain his revenge.
imdb.title: Mañana es para siempre
plot: After the Rebeca (Barbara) catches innocent Eduardo kissing his first love Fernanda, she sends him to a far away land. Years pass and tragedy brings him back, vengeance fills his heart towards the Elizaldo family. And the series unfolds as he developed a secret identity in order to gain his revenge.
